<doc id="305787" wikidata="Q13410384" url="?curid=305787" title="Pontoporiidae">
<text>Pontoporiidae is a family of toothed whales, containing the extant genus &quot;Pontoporia&quot;, and ten extinct genera. &quot;Pontoporia&quot; contains the sole extant species, the La Plata dolphin, which is endemic to South America.

