<text>The following lists events that happened during [[1901]] in [[Afghanistan]].

==Incumbents==
* Monarch – Abdur Rahman Khan (until October 1), Habibullah Khan (starting October 1)

==Events==
*October 3 – The &quot;amir&quot; Abdor Rahman Khan dies at Kabul. His eldest son, Habibullah Khan, succeeds to the throne.

==See also==
*History of Afghanistan

